        "content_4Prdgq": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why Us?",
            "subtitle": "<p>As one of Nepal’s leading producers of 100% genuine Mad Honey as private label, Medicinal Mad Honey collaborates with honey hunters all over Nepal to collect finest high quality mad honey. Within our packaging facilities in Kathmandu, we own an extensive storage,packing and honey filling facility. As a result, we provide a vertically integrated service that ensures your private label brand is nurtured to the highest international standards from your idea to the global brand.</p><p>\nMedicinal Mad Honey is proud to be the only Mad Honey collector and distributor in Nepal. In addition we sell Mad Honey wholesale USA and private label Mad Honey all around the world to retailers and resellers.</p>\n<p>\n<svg style=\"width:90%\" viewbox=\"0 0 645 127\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<g clip-path=\"url(#clip0_12106_31149)\">\n<path d=\"M122.84 58.9199C123.045 60.9572 123.162 63.0385 123.162 65.1344C123.162 98.0977 96.4429 124.817 63.4796 124.817C30.5163 124.817 3.79688 98.0831 3.79688 65.1344C3.79688 63.0239 3.89947 60.9426 4.11933 58.8906\" stroke=\"#723F19\" stroke-opacity=\"0.6\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path>\n<path d=\"M0.631078 48.4105C0.631078 48.4105 0.689706 48.3079 0.71902 48.2786C0.748333 48.2346 0.792304 48.2053 0.850931 48.176C0.909559 48.1466 0.968186 48.1173 1.05613 48.088L9.49848 44.9514C9.3226 44.9221 9.16137 44.8782 9.0148 44.8342C8.85358 44.7902 8.70701 44.7462 8.5751 44.7023L2.43387 42.7383L2.96152 41.082L13.0601 44.3065L12.7523 45.2739C12.7083 45.4205 12.635 45.5377 12.5618 45.6257C12.4885 45.7136 12.3712 45.7722 12.2247 45.8309L3.81162 48.9674C3.95819 48.9967 4.11941 49.0407 4.26598 49.0847C4.41255 49.1286 4.54446 49.158 4.67637 49.2019L10.8762 51.1806L10.3486 52.8368L0.25 49.6123L0.557794 48.6303C0.587108 48.5424 0.616422 48.4838 0.631078 48.4251V48.4105Z\" fill=\"#723F19\"></path>\n<path d=\"M14.2043 31.0712C14.8786 31.4523 15.4355 31.9213 15.8899 32.4