    "faq_fFAwqm": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_XEPM9x": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Where can I buy the best mad honey?",
            "answer": "<p>At Medicinal Mad Honey, we pride ourselves on delivering premium-quality mad honey sourced straight from the mountains of Nepal. Our direct partnerships ensure every jar is authentic, potent, and true to tradition.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_N3CVrW": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is the minimum order quantity for Mad Honey wholesale and bulk purchases?",
            "answer": "<p>The minimum order quantity for Mad Honey Wholesale and bulk is 10 kg , and the maximum depends on your specific requirements. As we are flexible , it doesn’t matter if you are starting or ordering large amounts, we will take care of you. Feel free to reach out to us and we will discuss the right option for your business.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_bJtL4k": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you offer Mad Honey wholesale pricing for resellers?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, Medicinal Mad Honey provides wholesale pricing for resellers and businesses that want to sell Mad Honey under their own brand and distribute or resell the mad honey in thor region.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_cU9Bya": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How can I purchase Mad Honey in bulk?",
            "answer": "<p>Mad honey is available for bulk purchase from suppliers who focus on wholesale distribution. If you're seeking reliable vendors that provide bulk pricing for large orders, Medicinal Mad Honey stands out as one of the most trusted Nepali brands for Mad Honey wholesale.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_B7TK9g": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What payment methods do you accept for wholesale orders?",
            "answer": "<p>We accept swift bank transfers and PayPal . Orders are sent once payment is confirmed.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_jAQTbx": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Where to Buy Honey Online?",
            "answer": "<p><br/>You can purchase authentic honey online from trusted websites and brands that prioritize quality and transparency. <a href=\"/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/\">Medicinal Mad Honey</a> is one of the best sources for rare, wild, and potent mad honey directly sourced from the Himalayan mountains.<br/>Whether you're a wellness enthusiast, a health store owner, or a traditional medicine practitioner, you can now buy premium mad honey in bulk directly from Nepal — with free shipping buckets, pails honey for sale available on every large-volume order.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_UzHYFV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I ensure the authenticity and quality of Mad Honey for my wholesale business?",
            "answer": "<p>At Medicinal Mad Honey, authenticity and quality are our top priorities. Our mad honey is sourced directly from himalayan regions and harvested by the honey hunting communities and we also do 3rd party lab testing to ensure it meets the highest standards. You can be assured that each batch of honey we supply is of the highest purity and potency.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_YwheeK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Where can I Buy Bulk Honey Online?",
            "answer": "<p><br/>You can purchase bulk honey online from trusted suppliers like Medicinal Mad Honey, which offers 100% pure, wild-harvested honey sourced from the Himalayan mountains. Their website provides direct options for bulk orders with worldwide shipping. <br/>Whether you're a wellness enthusiast, a health store owner, or a traditional medicine practitioner, you can now buy premium mad honey in bulk directly from Nepal — with free shipping buckets, pails honey for sale available on every large-volume order.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_6JXXi9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long does shipping take for wholesale orders?",
            "answer": "<p>For express shipping (DHL, UPS ) we offer 5-7 days, and cargo options are available for larger shipments for delivery time of 12-14 days worldwide.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_3UNgd6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How much does Mad Honey cost at wholesale?",
            "answer": "<p>Mad Honey costs depend on the brand’s names and their qualities . Medicinal Mad Honey is one of the best Nepali brands that supplies pure and authentic mad honey. We offer competitive rates for bulk and wholesale orders. For a personalized quote depending on your needs, get in touch with us directly.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_33KcJz": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you ship wholesale orders internationally?",
            "answer": "<p>We shipped orders all around the world . Depending on the destination and order size, shipping costs will vary.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_YjkEjC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Where can I buy Bulk Mad Honey Nepal?",
            "answer": "<p>You can buy bulk Mad Honey Nepal from Medicinal Mad Honey, a trusted Nepali brand that offers wholesale and bulk Mad Honey worldwide. We take a minimum bulk order of 10 kg. We provide quality honey for both individual customers and businesses. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_Gd6WJK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you provide a discount for long-term or bulk purchases?",
            "answer": "<p>For wholesale and loyal customers we offered customized pricing and special discounts.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_P9NyGb": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What's your return policy for Mad Honey wholesale orders?",
            "answer": "<p>We guarantee the quality of our authentic Mad Honey for wholesale partners. If you receive a damaged product, contact us within 7 days with photos for immediate replacement. While we don't accept returns on properly delivered products due to the nature of honey, we stand behind our premium Mad Honey quality with a satisfaction guarantee for your customers.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
